title: Deftones Discography + B-sides, Rares and Singles collection
description:
This is the complete discography of this amazing band, Deftones.
It contains the following albums:

1994 - Like (Linus)
1995 - 7 Words (Promo)
1995 - Adrenaline
1996 - The Crow (City of Angels)
1997 - Around the Fur
2000 - Acoustic in Las Vegas
2000 - Untitled
2000 - White Pony (Limited Edition)
2001 - Back to School (Mini Maggit) Maxi EP
2001 - The Ultimate Demo Collection
2003 - Deftones
2005 - B-sides and Rarities
2006 - Saturday Night Wrist (with 3 bonus tracks)
2010 - Diamond Eyes (Leaked Dub) (with 3 bonus tracks)
2011 - Oddities Demos
2012 - Koi no Yokan
